# UI Design System ‚Äî Linear-Inspired

## Principles
- **Light by default.** Clean white/off-white surfaces, no dark chrome.
- **Monochromatic base** with a single indigo accent (`primary`). Avoid mixing multiple accent colors in UI chrome.
- **Density over padding.** Compact elements: `h-7`/`h-8` inputs, `text-xs`/`text-sm` labels, tight gap spacing.
- **Borders, not shadows.** Use `border-border` or `border-border/50` for separation. Avoid `shadow-*` on cards.
- **Typography hierarchy** via weight + color, not size: `font-medium text-foreground` for labels, `text-muted-foreground` for secondary.

## Spacing & Sizing
- Page padding: `p-6`
- Section gaps: `space-y-5` or `space-y-6`
- Card content: `px-4 py-3` or `px-5 py-4`
- Inputs/buttons: `h-8` default, `h-7` for compact, `text-xs` or `text-sm`
- Icon size: `w-4 h-4` standard, `w-3.5 h-3.5` in compact contexts

## Components
```tsx
// Cards ‚Äî no shadow, subtle border
<Card className="bg-card border-border/50 hover:border-border transition-colors">

// Badges ‚Äî use color semantics
<Badge className="text-emerald-600 bg-emerald-50 border-0">   // success
<Badge className="text-amber-600 bg-amber-50 border-0">       // warning
<Badge variant="secondary" className="font-normal">           // neutral

// Inputs ‚Äî tinted muted background
<Input className="h-8 text-sm bg-muted/40 border-border/60 focus:border-primary/60" />

// Buttons
<Button size="sm" className="h-8 text-xs gap-1.5">  // primary action
<Button variant="ghost" size="sm" className="h-7 text-xs text-muted-foreground">  // secondary
<Button variant="outline" size="sm" className="h-7 text-xs border-border/60">    // tertiary
```

## Top bar
Always `sticky top-0 z-10 bg-background/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-border/40 h-14`.

## Sidebar
Slightly off-white (`var(--sidebar)`), `border-r border-border/50`. Active nav items: `bg-sidebar-accent text-foreground`. Inactive: `text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground`.

## Theme switching
- `next-themes` with `attribute="class"`, `defaultTheme="light"` ‚Äî supports `light`, `dark`, `system`
- `ThemeSwitcher` component at `@/components/theme-switcher` ‚Äî drop it where needed
- Never hardcode `dark:` variants that conflict with the CSS variable system; the `.dark` class on `<html>` drives everything

## What to avoid
- `shadow-md`, `shadow-lg` on cards or panels
- Colored backgrounds on hero sections or banners
- `text-lg` or larger for UI labels
- Rounded `rounded-xl` or `rounded-2xl` on small elements ‚Äî use `rounded-md`
